EN: The bank needs to see your valid proof of identification.

ZH: 请确认您的签证还在有效期。
EN: Please make sure your visa is still valid.

ZH: 我在机场遗失了护照。
EN: I lost my passport at the airport.

ZH: 他的身份证明已经过期。
EN: His identification has expired.

ZH: 请保管好您的重要证件。
EN: Please keep your important documents safe.

ZH: 我需要在办公室内接受入职培训，带上您的员工证。
EN: I need to undergo onboarding training in the office, so bring your employee ID. 

ZH: 为了预订航班，您需要提供您的护照和信用卡信息。
EN: In order to book a flight, you need to provide your passport and credit card information.
